{"heading":"The Saints will know the season of the Second Coming of Christ—Live the way Saints should live—Rejoice evermore—Do not despise prophesyings.","number":5,"verseCount":28,"verses":[[1,["But of the times and the seasons, brethren, ye have no need that I write unto you."]],[2,["For yourselves know perfectly that the ",["day",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Day of the Lord","tg/day-of-the-lord"],"; ",["Millennium, Preparing a People for","tg/millennium-preparing-a-people-for"],"."]]]," of the Lord so cometh as a ",["thief",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 106:4","dc-testament/dc/106.4"],"."]]]," in the night."]],[3,["For when they shall say, Peace and ",["safety",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Refuge","tg/refuge"],"."]]],"; then sudden destruction cometh upon them, as travail upon a woman with child; and they shall not ",["escape",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 1:2","dc-testament/dc/1.2"],"."]]],"."]],[4,["But ye, brethren, are not in ",["darkness",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 13:12 (12–13)","nt/rom/13.12"],"."]]],", that that ",["day",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 17:24","nt/luke/17.24"],"; ",["21:34","nt/luke/21.34"],"."]]]," should overtake you as a thief."]],[5,["Ye are all the ",["children",["study-note-ref","a",["GR sons. ",["TG Children of Light","tg/children-of-light"],"."]]]," of light, and the children of the day: we are not of the night, nor of darkness."]],[6,["Therefore let us not ",["sleep",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Sleep","tg/sleep"],"."]]],", as ",["do",["clarity-word"]]," others; but let us ",["watch",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Watch","tg/watch"],"."]]]," and be ",["sober",["study-note-ref","c",["GR sober, vigilant, circumspect. ",["TG Abstain","tg/abstain"],"."]]],"."]],[7,["For they that sleep sleep in the night; and they that be drunken are drunken in the night."]],[8,["But let us, who are of the day, be ",["sober",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Levity","tg/levity"],"."]]],", putting on the ",["breastplate",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 13:12","nt/rom/13.12"],"; ",["Eph. 6:11 (11–18)","nt/eph/6.11"],"."]]]," of ",["faith",["study-note-ref","c",[["Col. 1:4 (4–5)","nt/col/1.4"],"; ",["1 Thes. 1:3","nt/1-thes/1.3"],"."]]]," and love; and for an helmet, the ",["hope",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Hope","tg/hope"],"."]]]," of salvation."]],[9,["For God hath not appointed us to ",["wrath",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Thes. 1:10","nt/1-thes/1.10"],"; ",["1 Pet. 2:8 (6–8)","nt/1-pet/2.8"],"."]]],", but to obtain ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]]," by our Lord Jesus Christ,"]],[10,["Who died for us, that, whether we wake or sleep, we should ",["live",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Immortality","tg/immortality"],"."]]]," together with him."]],[11,["Wherefore ",["comfort",["study-note-ref","a",["GR exhort, console, encourage."]]]," yourselves together, and ",["edify",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Edification","tg/edification"],"."]]]," one another, even as also ye do."]],[12,["And we beseech you, brethren, to know them which ",["labour",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Leadership","tg/leadership"],"."]]]," among you, and are over you in the Lord, and admonish you;"]],[13,["And to ",["esteem",["study-note-ref","a",[["Philip. 2:29","nt/philip/2.29"],". ",["TG Respect","tg/respect"],"."]]]," them very highly in love for their work’s sake. ",["And",["clarity-word"]]," be at ",["peace",["study-note-ref","b",[["Mark 9:50","nt/mark/9.50"],"; ",["Rom. 15:5 (1–7)","nt/rom/15.5"],"; ",["D&C 20:54 (53–55)","dc-testament/dc/20.54"],"."]]]," among yourselves."]],[14,["Now we exhort you, brethren, ",["warn",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Warn","tg/warn"],"."]]]," them that are ",["unruly",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Thes. 3:11","nt/2-thes/3.11"],"."]]],", ",["comfort",["study-note-ref","c",["GR encourage, console."]]]," the ",["feebleminded",["study-note-ref","d",["GR faint-hearted, despondent."]]],", ",["support",["study-note-ref","e",["GR care for."]]]," the ",["weak",["study-note-ref","f",["GR infirm, doubting, timid."]]],", be patient toward all ",["men.",["clarity-word"]]]],[15,["See that none ",["render",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Retribution","tg/retribution"],"."]]]," ",["evil",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Forbear","tg/forbear"],"."]]]," for evil unto any ",[["man",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Enemies","tg/enemies"],"."]]],";",["clarity-word"]]," but ever follow that which is good, both among yourselves, and to all ",["men.",["clarity-word"]]]],[16,[["Rejoice",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]]," evermore."]],[17,[["Pray",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," without ceasing."]],[18,["In every thing give ",["thanks",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Communication","tg/communication"],"; ",["Thanksgiving","tg/thanksgiving"],"."]]],": for this is the will of God in Christ Jesus concerning you."]],[19,[["Quench",["study-note-ref","a",["GR Extinguish, Hinder, Suppress."]]]," not the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of","tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"],"; ",["Holy Ghost, Loss of","tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"],"."]]],"."]],[20,["Despise not prophesyings."]],[21,[["Prove",["study-note-ref","a",["GR Examine, Put to the test. ",["1 Jn. 4:1 (1–6)","nt/1-jn/4.1"],". ",["TG Study","tg/study"],"; ",["Test","tg/test"],"."]]]," all things; hold fast that which is good."]],[22,[["Abstain",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Abstain","tg/abstain"],"."]]]," from all ",["appearance",["study-note-ref","b",["GR kinds. ",["TG Apparel","tg/apparel"],"."]]]," of ",["evil",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Evil","tg/evil"],"."]]],"."]],[23,["And the very God of peace ",["sanctify",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Sanctification","tg/sanctification"],"."]]]," you wholly; and ",["I pray God",["clarity-word"]]," your whole spirit and soul and body be preserved blameless unto the coming of our Lord Jesus Christ."]],[24,["Faithful ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," he that calleth you, who also will do ",["it.",["clarity-word"]]]],[25,["Brethren, pray for us."]],[26,["Greet all the brethren with an holy ",["kiss",["study-note-ref","a",["JST 1 Thes. 5:26 … salutation."]]],"."]],[27,["I charge you by the Lord that this epistle be read unto all the holy brethren."]],[28,["The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," with you. Amen."]]],"volume":"nt"}